#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:592
msgid ""
"`RemotePath` represents a remote path bound to a `Connection` and returned "
"by `conn:path(path)`."
msgstr "`RemotePath` は `Connection` に紐づくリモートパスを表し、 `conn:path(path)` "
